    <item>
      <title>伊朗告诉联合国，如果以色列停止“冒险主义”，伊朗准备降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米拉卜杜拉希安在联合国表示，只要伊朗同意停止针对德黑兰利益的进一步军事行动，伊朗准备缓和与以色列的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨表示欧盟领导人将向乌克兰提供更多爱国者系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-to-send-ukraine-seven-more-patriot-missiles-as-allies-step-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯加大对能源基础设施和城市中心的导弹和无人机袭击力度，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨向其他欧盟领导人施压，要求其向乌克兰派遣更多爱国者防空系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-to-send-ukraine-seven-more-patriot-missiles-as-allies-step-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
